    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Juniperus montana are respiratory issues such as asthma, which is alleviated by its expectorant properties, urinary tract infections that can be cleared by its diuretic properties, and arthritis, which is alleviated by its anti-inflammatory compounds. Juniperus montana also exhibits antifungal properties, making it effective against fungal infections like candidiasis. Additionally, it has anti-inflammatory properties that help in treating skin inflammation, digestive issues such as diarrhea, and skin conditions like eczema. Furthermore, it has antimicrobial properties that make it effective against skin infections like acne, and it also exhibits antiseptic properties that aid in wound healing. Juniperus montana also has properties that help in managing diabetes, digestive problems, coughs, rheumatism, skin irritation, kidney stones, gout, and fever.",
